{"tid":1423139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[技能樹]新兵種：僧侶 正在開發，急需大量村民","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:55:56.000Z","uid":31076,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"888858e360c24aa4ce9e8ab76e0c28f95b990ee0","tid":1423139,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:59:42.000Z","msg":"利申只係重拾返童年回憶：<span style=\"color: green;\">世紀帝國（AOE）</span><br />\n<br />\n7月1日，有玩家出衝撞車；<br />\n7月14日，有玩家出高裝甲嘅條頓武士；<br />\n8月4日起，玩家開始識得出輕騎兵突襲資源據點，開始有成效<br />\n<br />\n只係最後嘅結果，都係喺官方玩家嘅重型投石車狂轟濫炸之下，兵力損失嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過只要控制得好，會發現AOE 最強嘅兵種，竟然係零攻擊力、只有35HP 嘅單位：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">僧侶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n僧侶憑藉嘅只係一把口，已經可以招降戰象之類嘅強大兵種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於一班願意付出時間嘅學生同村民，只要有人可以train up 同組織一下，好快就可以成為有戰鬥力嘅僧侶<br />\n<br />\n我敢肯定，向路過嘅中立勢力、以及對遊戲冷感嘅部隊<span style=\"color: orange;\">派發文宣，影響力遠遠不如有一班僧侶透過面對面傾計招降嚟得有效同深刻</span><br />\n<br />\n如果長時間可以安排到一定人數嘅僧侶企喺一齊，效果一定相當顯著<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">中立同冷感嘅單位，往往有大量黃金同資源</span>，對於遊戲戰役得以持續有決定性作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">8月10日，大埔區</span>好似有世紀帝國對戰嘅比賽，亦可以作為新兵種嘅試點<br />\n<br />\n小弟唔屬於任何AOE戰隊，冇組織冇大台，純粹只係一個普通網民<br />\n<br />\n但係自問知道少少人性，希望可以利用自己嘅經驗，<span style=\"color: gold;\">組織一下零散嘅村民</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我對AOE 嘅熱誠，大家可以睇我嘅舊post 嚟判斷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請有興趣成為僧侶嘅村民喺度留個tg，我會以充分保障到大家嘅方式嚟搵你地</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔得閒嘅都幫手推下討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4be87bbe2e2dfe09d6aa932b43985bc11f2683","tid":1423139,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"523f110094fff8a79415d83600cd8518c3032095","tid":1423139,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"官方玩家有無限資源秘技<br />\n<br />\n場比賽一定係難打<br />\n<br />\n所以更加要智取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c721c94bb42e312632956dd54457077997666e47","tid":1423139,"uid":33170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"Howdoyouturnthison"},{"pid":"77789f1c0e594e9c00ac240bac78d905cda8cc68","tid":1423139,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"811700693a5eb7257fdcbcc4f29f6df2f3f0ef12","tid":1423139,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"先講少少<br />\n<br />\n中立同無興趣玩遊戲嘅人一定係關注自己仲有冇得喺地圖上面採集資源<br />\n<br />\n而佢地未必會理解8月5日當日戰士堵塞通往資源採集點嘅道路<br />\n<br />\n僧侶可以先透過對路人微微鞠躬道歉令佢地態度軟化，再解釋官方玩家漠視200萬民意嘅事實<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，<span style=\"color: red;\">一旦戰士抗爭失敗，中立部隊嘅生計會如何被影響（例如明日大嶼、中資豆腐渣工程）</span><br />\n<br />\n人性，就係直接link 向佢地嘅利益"},{"pid":"141eb3f99631cdf6eca6c153484468983512d397","tid":1423139,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"當然如果有辦法可以搵到連儂牆嘅玩家對口就最好"},{"pid":"526327fac113adf98130a7e2b7987126d62c04da","tid":1423139,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:37:45.000Z","msg":"無名無姓，無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7555e4c15c1e831d2dd6677452029e90013a1091","tid":1423139,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"有無人想玩aoe"}]}